    function setAttributeOnload(object, attribute, val) {
      if(window.addEventListener) {
        window.addEventListener('load',
          function(){ object[attribute] = val; }, false);
      } else {
        window.attachEvent('onload', function(){ object[attribute] = val; });
      }
    }

}})();

          <div class="date-outer">
        
<h2 class='date-header'><span>miércoles, 16 de noviembre de 2022</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://i.ytimg.com/vi/giij0mNep-M/hqdefault.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='1060677886973972614' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='7963094130890810418' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='7963094130890810418'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/alemania-acciones-de-solidaridad-con-la.html'>ALEMANIA: Acciones de solidaridad con la CP-Sol Rojo de México</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7963094130890810418' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><iframe frameborder="0" height="270" src="https://youtube.com/embed/giij0mNep-M" width="480"></iframe>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Desde que se difundió la
noticia del asesinato de nuestro compañero Jesús Manuel García Martínez &#8220;Chu
Pau&#8221; hemos recibido distintas muestras de solidaridad por parte de
organizaciones democráticas y revolucionarias de nuestro país que han emitido
pronunciamientos y realizado movilizaciones conjuntas con nuestra organización
en exigencia de justicia y castigo a los culpables. </span></span><br /><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"></span></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Pero también desde otras latitudes
del mundo hemos recibido importantísimas muestras de solidaridad e
internacionalismo proletario confirmando las palabras del Presidente Mao Tse
Tung: <b>el internacionalismo es el espíritu del comunismo.</b></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><b><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheXGUYmh_1rwdOS_ZwkIeIXKOZo3LB7QBhiHtv8WqE8hDtve-NdBWIA5-feek1DwSDTd5O2bMjCE42kR2Sba32lqN0_tw3u_GI-yBupPXRSQyXTY1bu7FtNKObUnizdnX_Ft93oxLp9Z2FGNZQMyb3YKHlkvW47PimNNnHYTaQg7cX2F_lterUv00Z/s574/Berlin_Mexikanische_Genossen2.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="292" data-original-width="574" height="278" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheXGUYmh_1rwdOS_ZwkIeIXKOZo3LB7QBhiHtv8WqE8hDtve-NdBWIA5-feek1DwSDTd5O2bMjCE42kR2Sba32lqN0_tw3u_GI-yBupPXRSQyXTY1bu7FtNKObUnizdnX_Ft93oxLp9Z2FGNZQMyb3YKHlkvW47PimNNnHYTaQg7cX2F_lterUv00Z/w543-h278/Berlin_Mexikanische_Genossen2.jpg" width="543" /></a></b></span></p><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><b>&nbsp;</b></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Los compañeros de Alemania han
desplegado una intensa campaña de agitación y propaganda en torno al asesinato de &#8220;Chu Pau&#8221;,
militante de CP-Sol Rojo, quien fuera asesinado el pasado 27 de octubre en
Santa Cruz Tagolaba, así como también ha denunciado el asesinato del compañero
Filogonio Martínez Merino, miembro de Copudever, ocurrido el pasado 26 de octubre.&nbsp;</span></span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKVDNqqPidYjg6wBjXquMihh-7xl9yCBaD3Zc8UAQeCt30ZMei9rZyhWqbljSbvN6L4vNknAfeXqsWB8HBNvQbtnJHdpxENGuDHj9dSeT6E3SOLjUx1CzyPCRP2-0Ni8h2dHznqKkG4xykkErWY0OoZpBIVtXhBLWI6xeIYKqbSKmwh-lgtKIgsd-V/s3139/M%C3%BClheimMexikoMalung1.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="719" data-original-width="3139" height="133" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKVDNqqPidYjg6wBjXquMihh-7xl9yCBaD3Zc8UAQeCt30ZMei9rZyhWqbljSbvN6L4vNknAfeXqsWB8HBNvQbtnJHdpxENGuDHj9dSeT6E3SOLjUx1CzyPCRP2-0Ni8h2dHznqKkG4xykkErWY0OoZpBIVtXhBLWI6xeIYKqbSKmwh-lgtKIgsd-V/w583-h133/M%C3%BClheimMexikoMalung1.jpg" width="583" /></a></span></div><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"></span></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Ambos campesinos eran comuneros
en el Istmo y la Costa, respectivamente, y se oponían a la imposición de megaproyectos
imperialistas de despojo y muerte tal como lo son el Corredor Interoceánico del Istmo
de Tehuantepec y la presa hidroeléctrica Paso de la Reyna.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"></span></span></p><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVip3XRYepGWXPYizqrXePQ49z0sYtKQ38qYcFIpGNE5_T5mYoEcHDOZUtkt5G2rSUSbROdnM8_wr4eeUksbt16c94K6-nSet9tDmxiQ5Ar5PRpTjdQ2F-euInovayf_AzcUwsTSsFbl_1eqU8si9RC7606iGUJEcm-qFR92iLz5RJB943o4YcZRvy/s1000/Hamburg_Mexikanischen.JPG" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="667" data-original-width="1000" height="312" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVip3XRYepGWXPYizqrXePQ49z0sYtKQ38qYcFIpGNE5_T5mYoEcHDOZUtkt5G2rSUSbROdnM8_wr4eeUksbt16c94K6-nSet9tDmxiQ5Ar5PRpTjdQ2F-euInovayf_AzcUwsTSsFbl_1eqU8si9RC7606iGUJEcm-qFR92iLz5RJB943o4YcZRvy/w469-h312/Hamburg_Mexikanischen.JPG" width="469" /></a></span></div><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">A</span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">quí documentamos el más
reciente video realizado totalmente en español por los Comités de las Mujeres Rojas de Alemania y distintas
pintas que revolucionarios han realizado en varias ciudades de ese país.&nbsp;</span></span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8qN4XQ8ERmsTtEQw_IYVpvf1itCXV0DuqAD2fw63R8ss-xnINi4J2E0-wtXsFttivXSV1CJODugxIYjLTYVIG-BYjPV7UeN4sdPe_wBZiAHdN3Nw-ApLSCH-Yv0lN5dwsfzCk9Zzq6jyFM3eVkWAyvrOWS23oewzDAczZDf7AY8pNdCPKmnkZAMok/s3844/Bremen_Malung_f%C3%BCr_ermordete_Genossen_in_Mexiko_November_2022_1.JPG" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="2456" data-original-width="3844" height="300" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8qN4XQ8ERmsTtEQw_IYVpvf1itCXV0DuqAD2fw63R8ss-xnINi4J2E0-wtXsFttivXSV1CJODugxIYjLTYVIG-BYjPV7UeN4sdPe_wBZiAHdN3Nw-ApLSCH-Yv0lN5dwsfzCk9Zzq6jyFM3eVkWAyvrOWS23oewzDAczZDf7AY8pNdCPKmnkZAMok/w471-h300/Bremen_Malung_f%C3%BCr_ermordete_Genossen_in_Mexiko_November_2022_1.JPG" width="471" /></a></span></div><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"></span></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Desde México agradecemos
profundamente estas muestras de solidaridad e internacionalismo proletario y
saludamos estas importantes acciones documentadas en el sitio <a href="https://www.demvolkedienen.org/index.php/de/">Dem Volke Dienen</a>
(Servir al pueblo).</span></span></p><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjGGzr7zhdHdkFGbx2kIxOZGznwasf-zUoFEUeAgtlAozJakEctitXk5bBMA3zorb9D6VrG7QSirJNEeEF4GCmG6W2GTUm8elLvhLpEBQww94wM8l870stFnOfk5w1ZBe27aQtu3Rumsg64X9lctmVs_MDGWjjp67VAzMbL6nSmt3q0pcwyGwFqNCRc/s1651/M%C3%BClheimMexikoMalung2.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="992" data-original-width="1651" height="321" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjGGzr7zhdHdkFGbx2kIxOZGznwasf-zUoFEUeAgtlAozJakEctitXk5bBMA3zorb9D6VrG7QSirJNEeEF4GCmG6W2GTUm8elLvhLpEBQww94wM8l870stFnOfk5w1ZBe27aQtu3Rumsg64X9lctmVs_MDGWjjp67VAzMbL6nSmt3q0pcwyGwFqNCRc/w535-h321/M%C3%BClheimMexikoMalung2.jpg" width="535" /></a></span></div><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"></span><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;">

</span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><b><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&#161;Proletarios y pueblos
oprimidos del mundo, uníos!</span></b></span></p><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><b>

</b></span><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Century Gothic;"><b><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&#161;Viva el internacionalismo
proletario!</span></b></span></p>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>

<meta content='9161329152263533653' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='9161329152263533653'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/brasil-nota-do-cebraspo-sobre.html'>BRASIL:  Nota do CEBRASPO sobre a realização de audiência com a Comissão Interamericana de Direitos Humanos (CIDH) sobre os &#8220;Impactos da violência estatal em famílias de pessoas afrodescendentes no Brasil (1990-2022). </a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-9161329152263533653' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p>&nbsp;</p><div class="post-header">
<div class="post-header-line-1"></div></div><div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-5183618961593618536" itemprop="description articleBody"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiO8JyGRP-qnWllsZ4ItTe_MCapgaODcjBdnrWW2zALLAsKgXb9yM5RKjY-PC0MiHUuzgEviGbX9ey8ntSbDYOORxmYiakuo2m3gnjvj6SiIBanF2FLyY20c4fxEfsjMjPAYQeKS7Bc6nWc2ntSp2R_Pf7ijrYEBsOTlzuz45vD2kyKUGiIshdWTuMPSA" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img alt="" data-original-height="600" data-original-width="900" height="213" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiO8JyGRP-qnWllsZ4ItTe_MCapgaODcjBdnrWW2zALLAsKgXb9yM5RKjY-PC0MiHUuzgEviGbX9ey8ntSbDYOORxmYiakuo2m3gnjvj6SiIBanF2FLyY20c4fxEfsjMjPAYQeKS7Bc6nWc2ntSp2R_Pf7ijrYEBsOTlzuz45vD2kyKUGiIshdWTuMPSA" width="320" /></a></div><br /><br /><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;"></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEju4Ln8sNA0GyK6-Ct3b15Z6ftTDEmE89PlErQ65BQuLi0uRD8a8zCdk6uiJdf_-XG6zyLyTdfFcIIMXklstSap2x3RnAmpBUXxyNCDD1VV7hgEEyqh2-Kp6l4Xp4TU9wvX11v9GH5IbQDEOUX_rEjz9KAH731IkFMigi8AOYbGRumCaTqvCqcNKkOuOQ" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img alt="" data-original-height="533" data-original-width="800" height="213" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEju4Ln8sNA0GyK6-Ct3b15Z6ftTDEmE89PlErQ65BQuLi0uRD8a8zCdk6uiJdf_-XG6zyLyTdfFcIIMXklstSap2x3RnAmpBUXxyNCDD1VV7hgEEyqh2-Kp6l4Xp4TU9wvX11v9GH5IbQDEOUX_rEjz9KAH731IkFMigi8AOYbGRumCaTqvCqcNKkOuOQ" width="320" /></a></div><br /><br /><p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">O Centro Brasileiro de Solidariedade aos
Povos (CEBRASPO) foi convidado pelos movimentos de Mães e familiares de vítimas
de violência de Estado para colaborar com a realização de <span class="markedcontent">audiência com a Comissão Interamericana de Direitos Humanos
(CIDH) sobre os &#8220;Impactos da violência estatal em famílias</span> <span class="markedcontent">de pessoas afrodescendentes no Brasil (1990-2022)&#8221;.</span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Na audiência, as mães de vítimas de
violência estatal representaram em suas falas mães e familiares de todo o
Brasil. Grandes protagonistas da luta contra a criminalização da pobreza e
contra o racismo em nosso país, elas são as verdadeiras defensoras dos direitos
do povo nas favelas e periferias, denunciando os crimes de Estado, as mortes e
desaparecimentos forçados e exigindo direitos e garantias que possam combater a
impunidade e resguardar a vida e a saúde dos jovens e das famílias gravemente
impactadas pela violência estatal. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">As mães falaram sobre a violência letal
cotidiana das ações policiais por todo o Brasil, enquanto &#8220;processo de extermínio
da população pobre, preta, favelada e periférica&#8221;, que as autoridades públicas
buscam justificar e legitimar a partir da falácia da chamada &#8220;guerra às
drogas&#8221;. Elas destacaram em seus relatos a impunidade dos crimes de Estado, a
omissão do Ministério Público e do Sistema de Justiça que deveriam exercer o
controle da atividade policial, mas não o fazem e &#8220;também matam com a caneta&#8221;. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">As mães e familiares tem percorrido longo
e penoso caminho com a finalidade de punir os agentes públicos responsáveis
pela letalidade policial sob a forma de execuções e danos a populações,
inclusive crianças. Nesse caminho sofrem com todos os percalços,
frequentemente, resultantes de conluio entre as autoridades para o arquivamento
ou prescrição de processos. Ao levar a frente a sua luta são frequentemente
perseguidas e ameaçadas por forças de segurança com vistas a amedrontá-las para
manter os crimes na obscuridade.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Do luto à luta, as mães e familiares
sofrem com o grave adoecimento, enfrentando os impactos da violência estatal na
saúde. As mães seguem revivendo o sofrimento do luto e vivenciam a
revitimização a cada nova incursão policial nas favelas e periferias e
criminalização de seus filhos e territórios. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Após a violação brutal do seu &#8220;direito de
ser mãe&#8221;, elas tornam-se &#8220;estudiosas da impunidade, da criminalização e do
adoecimento perverso&#8221; causado pelo Estado, mostrando que no Brasil não há
efetivo respeito aos direitos humanos. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Por tudo isso, as mães cobram uma visita
direta da CIDH ao Brasil, para colher os depoimentos das mães, escutá-las,
constatar as denúncias e cobrar respostas concretas contra a impunidade dos
crimes de Estado. Elas reivindicam a efetiva implantação dos Planos de Direitos
Humanos no Brasil, demandam políticas públicas de reparação, bem como, a implantação
de um atendimento psicossocial com comissão multidisciplinar e conforme
definições e princípios instruídos pelos próprios familiares, </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Os representantes da Comissão
Interamericana e da ONU Direitos Humanos presentes manifestaram sua
solidariedade e profundo respeito às mães e familiares por sua dor e sua luta,
somando-se aos familiares nas colocações acerca da discriminação racial e de
classe, do perfilamento racial das populações periféricas por parte das
polícias e demandando ao Estado brasileiro a necessidade de investigações mais
criteriosas nos casos de mortes e desaparecimentos forçados por parte de
agentes estatais no Brasil. Além disso, exigem que o sistema de justiça ofereça
respostas efetivas aos familiares, destacando a necessidade do reconhecimento
da verdade, da justiça e da reparação como forma de permitirem que os
familiares possam seguir adiante. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">Mantendo-se firme ao lema de &#8220;defender o
direito do povo de lutar por seus direitos&#8221;, o Centro Brasileiro de
Solidariedade aos Povos segue apoiando a luta das mães e familiares do Brasil e
combatendo os crimes do velho Estado contra o povo. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><b>Toda solidariedade às mães e familiares
vítimas de violência estatal em todo o Brasil!</b></span></p><br /><p></p>
<div style="clear: both;"></div>
</div>

<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/internacional-ya-esta-lista-lucha-de.html'>INTERNACIONAL: Ya está lista Lucha de Dos Líneas revista Internacional Marxista-Leninista-Maoísta (Revolución Obrera)</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7058372098986226633' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><br /></p><article class="post-15804 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-mci tag-conferencia-internacional-mlm tag-movimiento-comunista-internacional tag-revista-lucha-de-dos-lineas" style="border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 40px; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline;"><div class="post-inner group" style="border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1;"><div class="clear" style="background-color: white; border: 0px; clear: both; color: #666666; font: inherit; height: 0px; margin: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; visibility: hidden; width: 0px;"></div><br /><div style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Portada-L2L-centr.jpg"><img height="382" src="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Portada-L2L-centr.jpg" width="271" /></a></div><br /><br /><br />Informamos a nuestros lectores que en el transcurso de la semana será publicada en inglés Lucha de Dos Líneas una nueva revista Internacional Marxista-Leninista-Maoísta<a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Portada-L2L.jpg"><img src="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Portada-L2L.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/contracapa-L2L.jpg"><img src="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/contracapa-L2L.jpg" /></a><br /><br /><br /><br /></div></article>

<a name='2334673308482674009'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/mexico-justicia-y-castigo-los-culpables.html'>MÉXICO: &#161;Justicia y castigo a los culpables!</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-2334673308482674009' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><br /></p><div class="post-header" style="background-color: #882222; color: seashell; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 10.8px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em;"><div class="post-header-line-1"></div></div><div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-2272201417736949004" itemprop="description articleBody" style="background-color: #882222; color: seashell; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 13.2px; line-height: 1.4; position: relative; width: 520px;"><p><br /></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh4hwZRxqe_kyxUvYqM8eFrtFwpcQ_dikLyK4aDuxog6E8bcyE5OIEp9_PY9jzruWkYmf6z48fXGMeQR9SwxGk4_mpIUWgqxxmsOzoe4ACtAIqFN1LpJQNqmhXJwfhEpQ81V9Hpc9LHRgfQAR4e54Kp6tQkAHEOpSCcWhpQUMlky9wvLwOQC4Q2tfPB/s1024/Chu%20Pau%20FORO.jpeg" style="color: #ffffcc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-decoration-line: none;"><img border="0" data-original-height="682" data-original-width="1024" height="266" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh4hwZRxqe_kyxUvYqM8eFrtFwpcQ_dikLyK4aDuxog6E8bcyE5OIEp9_PY9jzruWkYmf6z48fXGMeQR9SwxGk4_mpIUWgqxxmsOzoe4ACtAIqFN1LpJQNqmhXJwfhEpQ81V9Hpc9LHRgfQAR4e54Kp6tQkAHEOpSCcWhpQUMlky9wvLwOQC4Q2tfPB/w400-h266/Chu%20Pau%20FORO.jpeg" style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(102, 0, 0); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 1px 1px 5px; padding: 8px; position: relative;" width="400" /></a></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"><br /></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;;">Derivado del reciente asesinato del compañero Jesús Manuel García Martínez &#8220;Chu Pau&#8221;, así como del atentado contra nuestro dirigente regional, compañero Erick Sánchez Gutiérrez, el día de mañana 9 de noviembre están convocadas distintas actividades de protesta en las ciudades de Tehuantepec y Oaxaca, además de otros puntos donde habrá acciones de solidaridad.</span></p><span style="font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;;"></span><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;;">Aquí documentamos algunos de los carteles que se han difundido para las acciones.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify;"><span face="&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiOrAR4ZoI7mR4QwflxlC3qjA3QcnQHHLSllNA_-Q8Pxhm_jS1evmo5Se5BMRWLndunRZvj4fOdIYqHG2FPupxzKhlZOFARbU-0BULDkcd2G_8o79qA1nHne2WF9h4pj06M_wcNPWESr_62HRQ-9SzwkCdp7dHv8cztq1WA4pVJ-qD4GMmv8RUbId_v/s1024/Marchas%20simultaneas%203.jpeg" style="color: #ffffcc; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-decoration-line: none;"><img border="0" data-original-height="1024" data-original-width="768" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiOrAR4ZoI7mR4QwflxlC3qjA3QcnQHHLSllNA_-Q8Pxhm_jS1evmo5Se5BMRWLndunRZvj4fOdIYqHG2FPupxzKhlZOFARbU-0BULDkcd2G_8o79qA1nHne2WF9h4pj06M_wcNPWESr_62HRQ-9SzwkCdp7dHv8cztq1WA4pVJ-qD4GMmv8RUbId_v/w480-h640/Marchas%20simultaneas%203.jpeg" style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(102, 0, 0); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 1px 1px 5px; padding: 8px; position: relative;" width="480" /></a></div><br />&nbsp;<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhCXhywj-OAPmZ3VXnT47DEyp4s6n_Gw3VrCVQpqMgAeaKJiPK-0DfhVywFFxlG46fHme9YAX5uXUaCynbQzyoAypwWfX747bqjb8vd4vArWsz8I5Z4rzwDNV6h-2n0cbIBo7NmJU4GqIPNd_ACIlQVSnRNZlWiiGHsfycNo6CK5ckgoDITLaER6VIr/s2304/Marchas%20simultaneas%201.png" style="color: #ffffcc;           <div class="date-outer">
        
<h2 class='date-header'><span>domingo, 6 de noviembre de 2022</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='1060677886973972614' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='4638970716661603292' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='4638970716661603292'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/internacional-proposal-joint.html'>INTERNACIONAL: Proposal Joint Declaration English/Spanish LET&#8217;S DEVELOPE THE REVOLUTIONARY STRUGGLE AGAINST THE IMPERIALIST WORLD WAR PREPARATIONS! </a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-4638970716661603292' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="post-header">
<div class="post-header-line-1"></div><span style="font-size: small;"><b>LET&#8217;S
DEVELOPE THE REVOLUTIONARY STRUGGLE AGAINST THE IMPERIALIST
WORLD WAR PREPARATIONS!</b></span><span style="font-size: small;">
</span></div><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">&#8212;DECLARATION&#8212;</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">All
the imperialist countries proclaim to be defenders of freedom,
democracy and world peace. They all pretext to fight against
dictatorships and international terrorism. But indeed they are the
worst terrorist dictators in the world. They speak about peace but
frantically prepare for a new war of global robbery. They strengthen
the arms industry. They increase their arsenals. They mobilize huge
war machines mainly towards Eastern Europe. They sponsor the already
prolonged wars against the peoples of Palestine, Syria, Yemen. They
are inciting the outbreak of new reactionary wars in the Taiwan
Strait, on the Korean peninsula, in the East China Sea, on the
Ukrainian-Belarus border, on the sea border between Greece and
Turkey. NATO, commanded by Yankee imperialism, in Ukraine through the
puppet regime of Kiev, confronts its mercenary armies, weapons and
military chiefs, with the military might of Russian imperialism. Both
sides concoct pretexts to use nuclear weapons. The inter-imperialist
contradictions sharpened to the point that a new nuclear world war is
no longer a latent imperialist danger, but an imminent risk for the
existence of world society and its habitat.</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">The
world imperialist system, decadent and decomposed, in its inevitable
one-way march towards the grave, has unloaded on society the terrible
consequences of the increasingly acute world economic crisis, and
with it, has extended and deepened in all continents social, health
and environmental crises. For the insatiable imperialists, the
monopolization and accumulation of capital at the cost of the global
exploitation of social labor, the usurious export of financial
capital, the destruction of nature, the plundering of the oppressed
countries, is not enough. The crises of their system, mainly the
economic one, impel the imperialists to carry out a new division of
the already divided world. A new division that can only be achieved
by economic force, financial force, military force, the force of the
world war between a few imperialist countries in decline and others
fighting for world hegemony, as a product of the inexorable economic
law of the uneven development of the imperialist countries.</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">But
the same economic and social causes that push the imperialists to
wars of robbery, become unlivable, unbearable material conditions for
the slaves of capital, material conditions of the rebellion of the
exploited proletarians, peoples, nations and countries oppressed by
the monopolies and imperialist countries. And it is up to the
International Communist Movement to bring them the revolutionary
conscience, organize and transform the rebellions into a
revolutionary struggle against the common enemy: the world capitalist
system of oppression and exploitation.</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">It
is up to the communists to give an example of internationalist unity
and struggle against the preparations for a new imperialist world
carnage; join and coordinate efforts to promote the revolutionary
struggle of the proletarian armies in all countries against the
mobilization of troops and weapons for reactionary wars; construct a
common front with all the revolutionaries and democratic sectors that
oppose the support and military commitment of the lackey regimes with
their imperialist masters; reject and denounce as traitors the
opportunist satraps who, in the name of the proletariat and the
peoples, give support to one of the imperialist factions, when they
are all deadly enemies of the oppressed and exploited of the world;
relentlessly support the revolutionary struggle led by genuine
Marxist-Leninist-Maoist communists, mainly the people's war in India
that, together with other people's wars, today are the vanguard of
the World Proletarian Revolution, against imperialism and its
reactionary national watchdogs.</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">Imperialist
capitalism is in crisis! Long live Socialism and Communism!</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">Or
the revolution stops the war or the war unleashes the revolution!</span></p><span style="font-size: small;">
</span><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;">Workers
and peoples of the world, unite against imperialism!</span></p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"></p><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: serif; left: 118.105px; top: 706.992px; transform: scaleX(1.19175);"></span></b></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></b></span></p><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Communist Worker Union (mlm) Colombia</span></b></span></p><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Construction Committee of the Maoist Communist Party of Galicia</span></b></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="font-family: serif; left: 118.105px; top: 706.992px; transform: scaleX(1.19175);"></span></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Maoist Communist Party &#8211; Italy</span></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">you can sign this declaration&nbsp;</span></b></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #333333; font-family: Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">send  maoistroad@gmail.com&nbsp;</span></b></span></p><br /><br /><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p><p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span lang="es-ES"><b>&#161;IMPULSAR
LA LUCHA REVOLUCIONARIA CONTRA LOS PREPARATIVOS DE GUERRA MUNDIAL
IMPERIALISTA!</b></span></span></p>
<p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
&#8212;<span lang="es-ES">DECLARACIÓN</span><span lang="es-ES">&#8212;</span></p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span lang="es-ES">Todos los países imperialistas se proclaman
defensores de la libertad, la democracia y la paz mundial. Todos
pretextan luchar contra las dictaduras y el terrorismo internacional.
Pero en realidad son ellos los peores terroristas dictadores en el
mundo. Hablan de paz pero se preparan febrilmente para una nueva
guerra de rapiña mundial. Fortalecen la industria armamentista.
Agigantan sus arsenales. Movilizan descomunales máquinas de guerra
principalmente hacia el Este de Europa. Patrocinan las ya prolongadas
guerras contra los pueblos de Palestina, Siria, Yemen. Incitan al
estallido de nuevas guerras reaccionarias en el estrecho de Taiwan,
en la península de Corea, en el Mar de la China oriental, en la
frontera de Ucrania con Bielorrusia, en la frontera marítima entre
Grecia y Turquía. La OTAN comandada por el imperialismo yanqui, en
Ucrania a través del régimen títere de Kiev enfrenta sus ejércitos
mercenarios, armamentos y jefes militares, al poderío militar del
imperialismo ruso. De lado y lado urden pretextos para usar armas
nucleares. Las contradicciones inter-imperialistas se han ido
exacerbando hasta un punto, donde una nueva guerra mundial con armas
nucleares, ya no solo es un peligro imperialista latente, sino un
peligro inminente para la existencia de la sociedad mundial y de su
hábitat.     </span>
</p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span lang="es-ES">El sistema imperialista mundial, decadente y
descompuesto, en su inevitable marcha de no retorno hacia la
sepultura, ha descargado sobre la sociedad las terribles
consecuencias de la cada vez más aguda crisis económica mundial, y
con ella, ha extendido y profundizado en todos los continentes las
crisis social, sanitaria y ambiental. No basta para los insaciables
imperialistas la monopolización y acumulación de capital a cuenta
de la explotación mundial del trabajo social, de la usurera
exportación del capital financiero, de la destrucción de la
naturaleza, del saqueo de los países oprimidos. Las crisis de su
sistema, principalmente la económica, impele a los imperialistas a
realizar un nuevo reparto territorial del mundo ya repartido. Un
nuevo reparto que solo puede hacerse por la fuerza económica, la
fuerza financiera, la fuerza militar, la fuerza de la guerra mundial,
entre unos países imperialistas que ruedan hacia la decadencia, y
otros que lucha por la hegemonía mundial, como producto de la
inexorable ley económica del desarrollo desigual de los países
imperialistas.</span></p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span lang="es-ES">Pero las mismas causas económicas y sociales que
empujan a los imperialistas a las guerras de rapiña, se convierten
en condiciones materiales invivibles, insoportables, para los
esclavos del capital, condiciones materiales de la rebelión de los
proletarios, pueblos, naciones y países explotados y oprimidos por
los monopolios y países imperialistas. Y corresponde al Movimiento
Comunista Internacional llevarles la conciencia revolucionaria,
organizar y transformar las rebeliones en lucha revolucionaria contra
el enemigo común: el sistema de la opresión y la explotación
mundial capitalista.</span></p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span lang="es-ES">Corresponde a los comunistas dar ejemplo de unidad
y lucha internacionalista en rechazo a los preparativos de una nueva
carnicería mundial imperialista; juntar y coordinar esfuerzos para
promover la lucha revolucionaria de los ejércitos proletarios en
todos los países contra la movilización de tropas y armamento para
las guerras reaccionarias; hacer frente común con todos los
revolucionarios y sectores democráticos que se opongan al apoyo y
compromiso militar de los regímenes lacayos con sus amos
imperialistas; rechazar y denunciar como traidores a los sátrapas
oportunistas que a nombre de proletariado y de los pueblos, dan apoyo
a alguno de los bandos imperialistas, pues todos son enemigos a
muerte de los oprimidos y explotados del mundo; apoyar sin descanso
la lucha revolucionaria dirigida por los auténticos comunistas
marxistas-leninistas-maoístas, principalmente la guerra popular en
la India, que junto con otras guerras populares, hoy son la
vanguardia de la Revolución Proletaria Mundial, contra el
imperialismo y sus cancerberos nacionales reaccionarios.  </span>
</p>
<p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
&#161;El capitalismo imperialista está en crisis! &#161;Viva el Socialismo y
el Comunismo!</p>
<p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
&#161;O la revolución detiene la guerra o la guerra desata la
revolución!</p>
<p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
&#161;Proletarios y pueblos del mundo, uníos contra el imperialismo!</p><p align="center" class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><br /></p>
<p class="western" lang="es-CO" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
</p><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;">
<span style="font-size: small;"><b>Union Obrera Comunista (marxista-leninista-maoista) - Colombia<br /></b></span></p><p class="western" style="line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.21cm;"><span style="font-size: small;"><b>Comitado de Costruccion del Partido Comunista&nbsp; Maoista - Galicia</b></span></p><span style="font-size: small;"><b>Partido Comunista maoista-Italia</b></span>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>

<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='data:image/png;base64,' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='1060677886973972614' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='6321433194756822636' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='6321433194756822636'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/grecia-athens-solidarity-panel-for.html'>GRECIA: ATHENS: Solidarity panel for Professor Saibaba and the political prisoners in India - info ICSPWI</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-6321433194756822636' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><br /></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><img alt="312494032_145050741607907_1722429674749584961_n.jpg" height="390" src="data:image/png;base64," width="520" /></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;A panel&nbsp;concerning the pol</span><span style="background: white; color: black; font-size: 12pt;">itical
prisonersin India, event that dozens of people participated, was held by&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;">Bookstore-Cafe "Ektos ton Teichon" in Athens. The speakers
of the event, described the chronicle of persecutions, of the disabled
Professor GN Shaibaba, within the framework of the prefecture of
"antiterrorist" law UAPA. The panel tried to indicate the general
context within which operation "Green Hunt" takes place and the
fierce oppression of left and revolutionary voices in India. Operation
"Green Hunt", against the <span>&nbsp;</span>Communist Party of India(Maoist), and the
accusations against intelectuals as <span>&nbsp;</span>"urban naxals", is part of the
political landscape of violence and terrorism from the Indian Brahminical
regime.<span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;">Parts of the discussion showcased a variety of topics on the peoples
right movement, the Naxalite movement, the massive people's struggles in India
and the great contradictions within Indian society.<span></span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="background: white; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 12pt;">Events like this, are a firm display of internationalist
solidarity. Although, the most important political pressure that can be
exercised from abroad, <span>&nbsp;</span>towards the
Indian state, are massive struggles and demonstrations out of the Indian
state's embassies. In this direction, we address other political organizations
and forces, to shout for our opposition against the undemocratic prosecutions.<span></span></span></p>



<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 107%;">At the beginning
of the panel the following video was shown.<span></span></span></p>





<br /><br /><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;"><span>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9_YEosgQ2E">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9_YEosgQ2E</a></span></p>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>

<h2 class='title'>Bienvenido, bienvenida a Dazibao Rojo</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
Dazibao es una palabra china que nombra un cartel de grandes dimensiones, por lo general caligrafiado a mano, en el que se expresan denuncias, criticas o propuestas. Fue ampliamente usado por las masas durante la Gran Revolución Cultural Proletaria.<br/>Queremos que este espacio sirva para el debate, la critica y las propuestas para avanzar por el rojo sendero de la Revolución.<br/><br/>Participa !                                        email <a href="mailto:dazibaorojo@gmail.com">dazibaorojo@gmail.com</a><br/>
</div>

<h2>El camarada  Mao Tse-tung</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<img alt='El camarada  Mao Tse-tung' height='150' id='Image2_img' src='http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_nJRLUOQ-1lM/R8b4Di_M3jI/AAAAAAAAACM/B3k0wMosGKw/S150/mao+zhuxi+1958.jpg' width='93'/>
<br/>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
</div><div class='widget Text' data-version='1' id='Text2'>
<h2 class='title'>Citas del Presidente Mao Tse-Tung</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
Colocar los problemas sobre la mesa.<br/>Esto lo deben hacer no solo el "jefe  de la escuadra", sino tambien los miembros del comité. No se debe hablar a espaldas de la gente. Cuando surge algún problema, hay que convocar una reunión y colocar el problema sobre la mesa para discutirlo y tomar decisiones, y así el problema será resuelto.<br/>Si existen problemas y no se colocan encima de la mesa, permanceran sin resolver por largo tiempo y hasta pueden seguir pendientes durante años.<br/>Entre el "jefe de escuadra" y los miembros del comité debe haber mutua comprensión. Nada hay más importante que la comprensión, el apoyo y la amistad entre el secretario y los miembros del comité, entre el Comité Central y sus burós, así como entre éstos y los comités regionales del Partido.<br/><em></em><br/><br/><em>"Metodos de trabajo en los comités del Partido."(13 marzo de 1949 ). Obras Escogidas, tomo IV.</em><br/><br/>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>

    window.followersIframe = null;
    function followersIframeOpen(url) {
      gapi.load("gapi.iframes", function() {
        if (gapi.iframes && gapi.iframes.getContext) {
          window.followersIframe = gapi.iframes.getContext().openChild({
            url: url,
            where: document.getElementById("followers-iframe-container"),
            messageHandlersFilter: gapi.iframes.CROSS_ORIGIN_IFRAMES_FILTER,
            messageHandlers: {
              '_ready': function(obj) {
                window.followersIframe.getIframeEl().height = obj.height;
              },
              'reset': function() {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen("https://draft.blogger.com/followers.g?blogID\x3d1060677886973972614\x26colors\x3dCgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudBILdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQaByM0NDQ0NDQiByMzNzc4Y2QqByNlZWVlZWUyByM0NDQ0NDQ6ByM0NDQ0NDRCByMzNzc4Y2RKByM2NjY2NjZSByMzNzc4Y2RaC3RyYW5zcGFyZW50\x26pageSize\x3d21\x26origin\x3dhttp://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/");
              },
              'open': function(url) {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen(url);
              },
              'blogger-ping': function() {
              }
            }
          });
        }
      });
    }
